{"tid":297341,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係網吧玩CSO比班中學雞笑足半日!","createTime":"2017-06-25T11:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T15:46:52.000Z","uid":119688,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e49e389577dbe9a6119f25dfaf750d57a7f08e4","tid":297341,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"放假無聊 見好耐無去網吧<br />\n咪去包半日玩囉<br />\n<br />\n咁我見有CSO咪玩囉 玩落有幾好玩<br />\n興開之際 有班好高既中學雞係後面大大聲恥笑我<br />\n話仲玩CSO呢D垃圾GAME 仲笑我渣住把玩具槍仲要比人狂殺咁話喎<br />\n<br />\n咁我好嬲 心諗你班仆街玩咩咁巴閉<br />\n咁我就扮傻去廁所偷偷望 見佢地玩緊勁舞團D音樂開到幾大聲<br />\n仲有幾條MK妹(白滑長腿幾正)有講有笑<br />\n我當刻心諗行埋去恥笑你地咪又係玩舊MK GAME<br />\n<br />\n但我停一停諗一諗<br />\n驚打起上黎,我唔識用力打傷哂佢地<br />\n所以一樣扮經過返埋位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n算你班中學雞好彩 <br />\nBTW 你地長頭髮果條MK妹好撚正有冇IG/FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d217c4f4840fded4eb0868ddfe23422aaaaf510","tid":297341,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"從前有三隻蚊 佢地個名係 蝦.. 蝦..  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451e3c7399193b16f358e9148629558de97de3d4","tid":297341,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從前有三隻[b]<span style=\"color: red;\">蚊</span> 佢地個名係 蝦.. 蝦..  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝦"},{"pid":"8f7035c0e39b5beb01bf5e19b0395e3b16a39940","tid":297341,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>從前有三隻[b]<span style=\"color: red;\">蚊</span> 佢地個名係 蝦.. 蝦..  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><b